<br>
The time the minstrel got greedy, I was with a bard, he mezzed us both and then started attacking the bard.  An Eld walked up and bombed him so he ran back to attack Eld.  About that time his mez wore off so I finished him.  I have never seen a rabid minstrel before, but I enjoyed putting that dog down.<br>
<br>
By the way, my spec above is incorrect by one thing, I only had 12 in CS.  <br>
<br>
